Courtney Gains https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Courtney_Gains 0 Courtney Gains (born August 22, 1965) is an American actor best known for his portrayal of "Malachai" in the 1984 horror movie Children of the Corn, based on the short story by Stephen King.
